    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This issue appears to be exclusive to `LaserZap`, and it affects bleed, not just my mod code.\n\nRepro case: Give Minigunner in TD mod the `Laser` weapon, build a massive amount of them, write down or memorize the tick and render performance before firing, let them fire for 1-2 minutes or so, order them to stop, compare the tick/render ms with the values from before they started firing.\n\nEdit: If you let them fire long enough, you can probably trigger an OOM exception.\n"
